You're back.

503
00:27:46,769 --> 00:27:47,500
Look at her.

504
00:27:47,569 --> 00:27:48,609
She bought crabs...

505
00:27:48,670 --> 00:27:50,440
for Grandma Tang when she's away.

506
00:27:50,670 --> 00:27:52,109
Have fun. I'll go in first.

507
00:27:52,180 --> 00:27:52,980
Okay.

508
00:27:58,750 --> 00:27:59,450
Come on.

509
00:28:07,059 --> 00:28:08,220
How did a virus get in?

510
00:28:08,289 --> 00:28:09,160
